        {
          "height": 42,
          "id": 2,
          "name": "中华小面馆(China Noodle Restaurant)",
          "opacity": 1,
          "properties": [
            {
              "name": "description",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "这是一家中华传统小面馆，有中国各种面食。在这里可以吃饱喝足，恢复饥饿。\n(This is a traditional Chinese noodle restaurant featuring various types of Chinese noodles. Here, you can eat and drink to your heart's content and regain your strength.)"
            }
          ],
          "rotation": 0,
          "type": "building",
          "visible": true,
          "width": 43,
          "x": 354,
          "y": 115
        },
        {
          "height": 45,
          "id": 3,
          "name": "旅馆 (The Prancing Pony Inn)",
          "opacity": 1,
          "properties": [
            {
              "name": "description",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "这是一家温暖的木制旅馆，角落里有壁炉，可以用来休息和打听情报。\n(This is a cozy wooden inn. There is a fireplace in the corner, which can be used for resting and gathering information.)"
            }
          ],
          "rotation": 0,
          "type": "building",
          "visible": true,
          "width": 62,
          "x": 257,
          "y": 112
        },
        {
          "height": 44,
          "id": 5,
          "name": "武器防具店(Weapon and Armor Store)",
          "opacity": 1,
          "properties": [
            {
              "name": "description",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "这是一家武器防具店，在这里可以购买各类剑、法杖、枪、刀、投掷类等武器，以及盾、护甲等防具。\n(This is a weapons and armors store. Here, you can purchase various types of swords, wands, guns, knives, throwing weapons, as well as shields and armor for protection.)"
            }
          ],
          "rotation": 0,
          "type": "building",
          "visible": true,
          "width": 63,
          "x": 160,
          "y": 211
        },
        {
          "height": 44,
          "id": 6,
          "name": "魔法药水店(Magic Potion Shop)",
          "opacity": 1,
          "properties": [
            {
              "name": "description",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "可以购买各类魔法药水，包括恢复类、增益类和负面攻击类药水。同时也可以找店内女巫进行占卜。\n(You can purchase various types of magic potions, including those for healing, enhancing, and dealing negative damage. At the same time, you can also consult the witch in the store for a divination.)"
            }
          ],
          "rotation": 0,
          "type": "building",
          "visible": true,
          "width": 44,
          "x": 259,
          "y": 210
        },
